text: Amrinder Singh (born 1993) is an Indian footballer. Amrinder or Amarinder Singh may also refer to: *Amarinder Singh (born 1942) is an Indian politician, chief minister of Punjab, India * Amrinder Singh Gill (born 1976), known as Amrinder Gill, Punjabi singer-actor *Amrinder Singh Raja Warring (born 1977), Indian politician, Member of Punjab Legislative Assembly for Gidderbaha
title: Amrinder Singh (disambiguation)
